Module 1:- Login and Registration
Allows the student to login and register in CampusHub. 
Checks for valid Credentials to enter them to CampusHub.

Module 2:- Profile Management
Stores the student and teacher details.
Customer can edit their own credentials.

Module 3:- Skills
Tracks the skills of students.
students can edit their skills on their profile.

Module 4:- Projects
Tracks the projects of students.
stores a record of projects the student has built.

Module 5:- Academics
Tracks the academic performance of students.
Customer can see their subjects,CGPA,marks.

Module 6:- Placement Preparation
Tracks the placement preparation activities of students.
Shows that each students coding skills,aptitude skills and interview preparation status.

Module 7:- Applications
Tracks the applications submitted by students for various opportunities.
lists the applications submitted by students for internships,jobs and other opportunities.

Module 8:- Progress
Shows overall progress of students in various aspects like academics,skills,projects and placement preparation.

Module 9:- parent and student follow up
Every this about student can be shared to parents.